					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p138393">Re: What does it mean to &quot;hack&quot; a game?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=138393#p138393"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Jan 01, 2015 12:16 am&nbsp;</div></td>
